      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>春节零食商城</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        background-color: #F4F4F5;\n        color: #333333;\n    }\n    header {\n        background-color: #D32F2F;\n        padding: 10px;\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: center;\n        align-items: center;\n    }\n    header input {\n        padding: 8px;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px 0 0 4px;\n        width: 70%;\n    }\n    header button {\n        padding: 8px 12px;\n        border: none;\n        background-color: #FFD700;\n        color: #333333;\n        border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    nav {\n        background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        padding: 10px;\n    }\n    nav ul {\n        list-style: none;\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0;\n        display: flex;\n        overflow-x: auto;\n    }\n    nav li {\n        padding: 8px 12px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        white-space: nowrap;\n    }\n    section {\n        background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        margin: 10px;\n        padding: 10px;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    #product-gallery img {\n        max-width: 100%;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    #price-info span {\n        margin-right: 10px;\n        display: inline-block;\n    }\n    #price-info .current-price {\n        color: #D32F2F;\n        font-size: 1.2em;\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n    #price-info .original-price {\n        text-decoration: line-through;\n        color: #999;\n    }\n    #price-info .promo-tag {\n        background-color: #FFD700;\n        padding: 2px 6px;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        font-size: 0.9em;\n    }\n    #countdown-timer {\n        text-align: center;\n        background-color: #FFEFD5;\n    }\n    #coupon-section div {\n        background-color: #FFD700;\n        padding: 10px;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    #coupon-section button {\n        margin-top: 8px;\n        background-color: #D32F2F;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n        border: none;\n        padding: 8px 12px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    #spec-selector label {\n        display: block;\n        margin-bottom: 5px;\n    }\n    #spec-selector select {\n        padding: 6px;\n        width: 100%;\n    }\n    #comment-filter div {\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-around;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #comment-filter ul {\n        list-style: none;\n        padding: 0;\n    }\n    #buy-button {\n        width: calc(100% - 20px);\n        margin: 10px;\n        padding: 12px;\n        background-color: #D32F2F;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        font-size: 1.1em;\n    }\n    #modal-cart {\n        position: fixed;\n        bottom: 0;\n        left: 0;\n        right: 0;\n        background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        box-shadow: 0 -2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        padding: 10px;\n    }\n    #modal-cart div {\n        margin-bottom: 8px;\n    }\n    #modal-cart button {\n        width: 100%;\n        padding: 10px;\n        background-color: #D32F2F;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    #promotion-stock-tip p {\n        text-align: center;\n        font-size: 0.9em;\n        color: #D32F2F;\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<header id=\"search-bar\">\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"搜索春节零食或相关产品\">\n    <button>搜索</button>\n</header>\n\n<nav id=\"nav-bar\">\n    <ul>\n        <li>饼干</li>\n        <li>糖果</li>\n        <li>坚果</li>\n        <li>茶类</li>\n        <li>礼包</li>\n    </ul>\n</nav>\n\n<section id=\"product-gallery\">\n    <img src=\"product.jpg\" alt=\"产品外观图\">\n    <p>精选优质材料，香酥美味，春节送礼佳品。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"price-info\">\n    <span class=\"current-price\">¥99</span>\n    <span class=\"original-price\">¥129</span>\n    <span class=\"promo-tag\">限时优惠</span>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"countdown-timer\">\n    <span>00:12:35</span>\n    <p>限时促销进行中，赶快抢购！</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"coupon-section\">\n    <div>满200减20优惠券</div>\n    <button>立即领取</button>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"spec-selector\">\n    <label for=\"spec\">请选择规格：</label>\n    <select id=\"spec\">\n        <option>10包</option>\n        <option>20包</option>\n        <option>30包</option>\n    </select>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"comment-filter\">\n    <div>\n        <button>好评</button>\n        <button>中评</button>\n        <button>差评</button>\n    </div>\n    <ul>\n        <li>零食很新鲜，包装精美。</li>\n        <li>味道不错，但快递有点慢。</li>\n    </ul>\n</section>\n\n<button id=\"buy-button\">\n    <span>立即购买</span>\n</button>\n\n<aside id=\"modal-cart\">\n    <div>购物车中有 2 件商品</div>\n    <div>总价：¥198</div>\n    <button>确认支付</button>\n</aside>\n\n<section id=\"promotion-stock-tip\">\n    <p>库存有限，售完即止</p>\n</section>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
    }
